T1  - Do founders matter? A study of executive compensation, governance structure and firm performance
AU  - He, Lerong
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 23
IS  - 3
SP  - 257
EP  - 279
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/05/01/
SN  - 0883-9026
