T1  - The evolution of growth intentions: Toward a cognition-based model
AU  - Dutta, Dev K.
AU  - Thornhill, Stewart
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 23
IS  - 3
SP  - 307
EP  - 332
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/05/01/
